ðŸ“š 13. MySQL Architecture Summary

+-------------------------------------+
|            SQL Layer                |
| (Parser, Optimizer, Executor)       |
+-------------------------------------+
|         Storage Engine Layer        |
| (InnoDB, MyISAM, Memory, etc.)      |
+-------------------------------------+
|         Data & Log Files            |
| (.ibd, .frm, .log, etc.)            |
+-------------------------------------+


